INSERT INTO
    catch_main_areas (
    catch_main_area_id,name,longitude,latitude
   )
SELECT
    *
FROM
    UNNEST(
        $1::INT[],$2::TEXT[],$3::DECIMAL[],$4::DECIMAL[]
    )
        ON CONFLICT (catch_main_area_id) DO UPDATE SET name = COALESCE(catch_main_areas.name, EXCLUDED.name),longitude = COALESCE(catch_main_areas.longitude, EXCLUDED.longitude),latitude = COALESCE(catch_main_areas.latitude, EXCLUDED.latitude)
